events.name: ノラが調べられる場所

parameters: Thief Nora: Sniff sniff... I found a strange smell!
Clea: Is this a diary, I wonder...

Clea: There's blood all over it, and some strange symbols...
I wonder what it could be.

Mage Relm: Please show it to me! If I'm a genius, I might be
able to decipher it... um...

Mage Relm: This is an ancient language from the Valto
region... anomaly... conceal oneself... deep within the
Devil's Cave... I see.
Clea: Could this be some kind of code?

Mage Relm: The Devil's Cave... There might be a place like
that nearby.
Mage Relm: How about we go and check it out?
Thief Nora: But we don't know the location, right...?

Mage Relm: Let's go to my room at the Magic Academy! I have
books related to the Devil's Cave stored there, you know!
Priestess Sophia: I wonder what's wrong, Clea-chan?

Clea: Let's go to the Magic Academy. Thank you, Relm-san and
Nora-san.

Mage Relm: You should be more grateful! After all, you had
the privilege of witnessing this genius revelation up close!

Mage Relm: Even if you call it a clue... I can't even begin
to consider the whereabouts of the ogre.

Cleric Sophia: Yes, that's right. I don't have any
familiarity with this place either.

Thief Nora: Um~ If it's me, I might be able to search for
clues using my sense of smell.

Clea: No matter what kind of clue it is, Nora-san, please
help us out.
Thief Nora: Yes, leave it to me!
